{{Infobox item |name = Argencium |image = XC3 key item.png |caption = "A unique silverish mineral that grows on backs of a rare species of Ropl." |type = Key Item |xc3rarity = Common |source = [[Argent Ropl]], during ''[[For the Sake of Keepsakes]]'' |sell = N/A }} '''Argencium''' is a DLC [[Key Item]] in {{XC3}}. It can be obtained by defeating the [[Argent Ropl]] during the [[Quest (XC3)|Quest]] ''[[For the Sake of Keepsakes]]''. {{clr}}
== Trivia == * The name of Argencium is likely a reference to [[Argentum]] from {{XC2}}. {{xc3 stub}}
