{{Infobox quest |name = Arts and Crafts |image = XC3 Challenge Battle Mode.png |description = "Here, can use Arts one after other! Special event of Archsage festival! But enemy also use, just for kicks." |giver = [[Nopon Archsage]] |location = [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]] |prereqs = Main story completed |difficultyCB3 = 3 |rewards = }} '''Arts and Crafts''' is a Time Attack [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] in {{XC3}}. It can be received from [[Nopon Archsage]] in the [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]], available as downloadable content from the second part of the Expansion Pass. Clearing this challenge with at least an A rank for the first time will unlock the Swimwear B outfit for [[Sena]].
